{
  "stem": "24409.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was a reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the reason was also to try to get as many Jews as possible to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not only the humanitarian element that caused me to act.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in 1936, a man came to my office.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was a young lawyer, then-- an apprentice lawyer, but for all practical purposes, you were a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For six years, you had to work, supposedly, as an apprentice, before you could work under your own name.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a man came to my office with a letter from Dr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Wolfgang von Weisl, who was a leader, internationally-recognized leader, of Zionism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, this man has an interesting suggestion, listen to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I listened to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at that time, part of Northern Africa was in Italian hands.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was an Italian colony, Libya and-- and-- I think Libya, and I don't know how the other part of North Africa was called at that time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he intended-- Mussolini intended to make it a big show and hold a big massive fair, to the-- to-- to-- to the-- to be the massive fair of Libya.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the suggestion was-- by this man-- he was a Palestinian who has come from Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And a very interesting type.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was a very committed Jew, and also a real adventurer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And his suggestion was that we rent, that we take a boat-- rent a boat-- and say that we are going to the Fiera di Tripoli.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The Fiera di Tripoli is what it was called.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Tripoli [INAUDIBLE] and Libya were two provinces, then, of Italian rule.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we go to the Fiera di Tripoli, put Betarim on it, members of the active Jewish movement-- Jewish movement in which I have been active.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
